div.data-section-title: So easy to use that it’s hard to explain.

div.h1: Tumblr is so easy to use that it’s hard to explain.
div.p: We made it really, really simple for people to make a blog and put whatever they want on it. Stories, photos, GIFs, TV shows, links, quips, dumb jokes, smart jokes, Spotify tracks, mp3s, videos, fashion, art, deep stuff. Tumblr is 378 million different blogs, filled with literally whatever.

Turns out that when you make it easy to create interesting things, that’s exactly what people do. All those great, random blogs your friends send you, those are Tumblr blogs. We’ll help you find and follow blogs like that, and we’ll help other people find and follow yours.

div.data-section-title: You already know how this works.

div.h1: You already know how this works.

        var title = '';

        // If tag.is_query, we manufactured this tag in the client

            // This ifalls back to the plain escaped tag.
            title = tag.hilite_tag || tag.escaped_tag;
        }

        if(!tag.featured && !tag.unread_count) result_class += ' no_count';

        if(tag.is_featured) result_class += ' is_featured';

        tag.url = tag.url.replace('/tagged/', '/search/');
